ON 25 June 2026
Today's topic was Network Devices
Today, I got a tour of the company's server room and main distribution frames. 
Instead of just reading about hardware, I worked physically with enterprise-grade equipment.
The senior engineers showed me their rack-mounted Switches (handling layer 2 internal office traffic) and edge Routers connecting us to our ISPs.
I also got to look at the management interface of their hardware firewalls, which strictly control what traffic is allowed in and out of the corporate network.
